description.plain:
Olajide “JJ” Olatunji (born 19 June 1993), better known as KSI, is a British YouTube star, rapper, boxer, actor and co-founder of the entertainment collective known as the Sidemen. He was born and raised in Watford, Hertfordshire, England. His main channel, “KSI,” is now his official artist channel. KSI is short for his YouTube channel name KSIOlajideBT, which derives from “KSI” (a Halo clan), also meaning knowledge, strength, and integrity, his name, and “BT,” meaning “British Telecom.”

KSI started doing YouTube in 2010 and has now grown to be one of the most subscribed YouTubers in the world. Apart from being a YouTube sensation, he has also become an artist.

Back in the day when KSI started doing YouTube, he was already making songs in his videos. The first song was his Call of Duty 1v5 Rap. At the time, he had only 50 subscribers.

On 12 April 2019, KSI and Randolph released their collaborative album New Age, the name resembling how they are creating a new style of music, which is portrayed through the different styles of beats used for the tracks. The album features guest appearances from Talia Mar, JME, and Quadeca.

On 22 May 2020, KSI dropped his debut solo album, titled Dissimulation. The album explored JJ’s own inner self and conflict with not just himself, but those around him, something he has said he found difficult exploring. The album features guest appearances from Offset from the hip-hop trio Migos, Smokepurpp, Lil Pump, Swarmz, Tion Wayne, Jeremih, Trippie Redd, Aiyana-Lee, the first official artist signed to his record label “The Online Takeover”, S-X, Lil Baby,  and Rick Ross. Three days later, on 25 May 2020, KSI dropped the deluxe with additional guest appearances from AJ Tracey, Rich the Kid, Randolph, and Crypt.

songs.title: Lamborghini

description.plain:
After two featured appearances on songs with Sway, “Lamborghini” is his first rap effort with him as the star, although he does pass the mic to P Money so he can spit his own verse.

This song has since been KSI’s most popular song, gathering more than 33 million streams on Spotify and over 100 million views on YouTube.

songs.title: Little Boy

description.plain:
“Little Boy” is KSI’s response to W2S’s diss track about him. It was previewed at the end of his collaboration song with RiceGum, “Earthquake”, which was a response to Behzinga’s diss track.

This song was teased while KSI and S-X were together recording after his New Age album had come out. This song features S-X, Rick Ross & Lil Baby, which KSI alluded to when he once said he has some ‘big features.’

This was JJ’s walkout song to the fight with S-X and Rick Ross performing in the ring.
